{"tid":1407254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有人假扮和理非指摘前線 再比唔知乜野事既阿叔打","createTime":"2019-08-04T15:03:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T15:42:22.000Z","uid":34047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c81f2e6172f95e69a850f249d1ed2ef947dadfb9","tid":1407254,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:03:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2508791889183963/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F420361564693683%2Fposts%2F2508791889183963%2F&d=wovbC19maxltJNBkbBY4lCbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=82db7c96\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2508791889183963/</a><br />\n<br />\n講真 一向都話各有各做<br />\n和理非唔認同既可以提意見<br />\n但唔駛咁樣出黎大大聲指摘<br />\n仲要係危急關頭<br />\n同埋點火係想set防線轉場而唔係用黎攻<br />\n唔係話一定支持用火<br />\n但危急關頭用火可以幫前線甩身<br />\n同埋呢個扮和理非既人有冇用返同一把尺鬧黑警<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得真和理非唔會咁<br />\n只會勸導但唔會咁樣鬧<br />\n當然 前線有野做得唔好係可以批評<br />\n但唔係咁樣響set緊防線既緊急關頭時比你咁樣鬧"},{"pid":"9593330a05ebe72bded0f7d5805956ff20baa57b","tid":1407254,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:04:40.000Z","msg":"另外 失驚無神打佢果個白衫又係乜野事"},{"pid":"113e70b836c1908abe9b6d952b88a024d22320e4","tid":1407254,"uid":163504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:07:31.000Z","msg":"阿伯好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520b5e0cb6712fa96ceaac3c3613f11684ccd821","tid":1407254,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"113e70b836c1908abe9b6d952b88a024d22320e4","tid":1407254,"uid":163504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:07:31.000Z","msg":"阿伯好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:42:22.000Z","msg":"但其實唔知佢咩野陣形<br />\n係藍絲定勇武<br />\n不過佢冇郁手打其他前線"}]}